Dan Mungai
Data Expert
WritingHub Africa Ltd

Bio

Dan Mungai is a data analysis, visualization and modeling enthusiast by use of R programming software as well as SPSS. Trained in the field of ecology, environmental science and fisheries, Data analytics is crucial to his field. The training background and enthusiasm in data analytics makes Dan fit to undertake any data analysis in the field of natural sciences.

Education

Kisii University, Kisii Campus | Kisii, Kenya

MSC in Fisheries Management | September 2017 - May 2019

Datacamp Online | Online, Kenya

MSC in Data Science | September 2018 - May 2020

Experience

KMFRI - Kisumu | Ecosystem Modeling of Lake Victoria | 2018 - 2020

WritingHub Africa Ltd | Data Analyst | July 2020 - present
